aduate/image/img_1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div><span>クレーン設計</span><span>Noritaka.S</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"branding-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/image/img_2.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div><span>品質保証</span><span>Yudai.A</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"branding-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/image/img_3_shunya.T.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div><span>サービス設計</span><span>Shunya.T</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"branding-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/image/img_4.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div><span>生産技術</span><span>Ren.U</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"branding-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/image/img_5_miho.Y.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div><span>営業</span><span>Miho.Y</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"branding-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/image/img_6_haruki.M.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div><span>アフターサービス</span><span>Haruki.M</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\n\t<div class=\"section-recruit section-company\">\n\t\t<div class=\"accessory-8 delay\"></div>\n\t\t<div class=\"company-left\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"company-image\">\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/image/img_top_link_jobdescription.jpg\" class=\"delay\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"accessory-1 delay\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"accessory-2 delay\"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"company-right delay\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"recruit-title recruit-title-left\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2>JOB<br>DESCRIPTION</h2>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"recruit-subtitle\">募集要項</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"recruit-title-en\">01. DESCRIPTION</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"description\">スケールの大きなモノづくりにぜひチャレンジしてみませんか？<br>\n当社に応募いただくうえで基本的な募集条件（募集対象、人数、職種、給与、福利厚生など）はこちらをご参照ください。</p>\n\t\t\t<!-- <div class=\"d-flex justify-content-center\"> -->\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"more-3\" href=\"/recruit/job-description.html\"><span>READ MORE</span><span></span></a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\n\t<div class=\"section-recruit\" id=\"section-works\">\n\n\t\t<div class=\"works-block\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"works-back-text delay\">Recruitment<br>message</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"works-back delay\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"accessory-9\"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<!--div class=\"works-back-image\"></div-->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"accessory-3 delay\"></div>\n\t\t\t<!-- <div class=\"accessory-7 delay\"></div> -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"recruit-title recruit-title-left delay\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2>RECRUITMENT<br>MESSAGE</h2>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"recruit-subtitle\">採用メッセージ</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"recruit-title-en\">02. MESSAGE</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"works-block-1 delay\">\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"description\">当社における採用の考え方についてまとめています。</p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex justify-content-start\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"more-3\" href=\"/recruit/newgraduate/message.html\"><span>READ MORE</span><span></span></a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /.works-block -->\n\n\t\t<div class=\"works-block\">\n\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/image/img_top_link_message.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t</div><!-- /.works-block -->\n\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"section-recruit section-company\">\n\t\t<div class=\"accessory-8 delay\"></div>\n\t\t<div class=\"company-left\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"company-image\">\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/image/img_top_link_voice.jpg\" class=\"delay\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"accessory-1 delay\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"accessory-2 delay\"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"company-right delay\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"recruit-title recruit-title-left\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2>EMPLOYEE'S<br>VOICE</h2>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"recruit-subtitle\">先輩社員の声</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"recruit-title-en\">03. VOICE</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"description\">当社で働いている社員たちをご紹介します。みんな日頃から明るく前向きで、業務に対して真摯に取り組んでいます。</p>\n\t\t\t<!-- <div class=\"d-flex justify-content-center\"> -->\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"more-3\" href=\"/recruit/newgraduate/interview/index.html\"><span>READ MORE</span><span></span></a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\n\t<div class=\"section-recruit\" id=\"section-figures\">\n\n\t\t<div class=\"figures-back-text delay\">DATA <br>FIGURE</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"figures-back delay\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"accessory-4\"></div>\n\t\t\t<img class=\"figures-back-image\" src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/image/bg_img.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"accessory-5 delay\"></div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"recruit-title delay\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"recruit-title-en\">04. HITACHI PLANT MECHANICS IN FIGURES</div>\n\t\t\t<h2>数字で知る<br>日立プラントメカニクス</h2>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"figures\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<!--div class=\"col-12 d-flex flex-column\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"figure-item figure-item-wide delay\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex justify-content-between\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"figure-thumb figure-thumb-large\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>天井クレーンの歴史</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/image/icon_1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex justify-content-center flex-column\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"figure-data figure-data-large\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>100</span>年以上\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"figure-remarks-2\">※初号機は1909年製造</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div-->\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-6 col-md-12 d-flex flex-column\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"figure-item delay\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex justify-content-between\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"figure-thumb\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>天井クレーン<br>の歴史</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/newgraduate/image/icon_1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=